557
00:49:11,210 --> 00:49:15,540
To je v poriadku. Nemám rada morské slimáky.

558
00:49:15,540 --> 00:49:18,920
A neprišla som sme kvôli zrazu.

559
00:49:24,940 --> 00:49:29,110
